dfischer.proxysniffer

Class ProxySnifferVarSourceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>
      • java.util.Hashtable
        • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxySnifferVarSourceHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map

    public class ProxySnifferVarSourceHandler
extends java.util.Hashtable
    Generic var source handler for all kinds of var sources.

    Hint: Note that a var source contains only the var source definition by itself but does not contain any var extractor instructions.

    See Also:
    (abstract generic class), ProxySnifferVarSourceRecordedUrl, ProxySnifferVarSourceTextfile, ProxySnifferVarSourceUserInputField, ProxySnifferVarSourceConstantValue, ProxySnifferVarSourceLoadtestPlugin, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript, ProxySnifferVarSourceWebSocketPlugin, ProxySnifferVarSourceWebSocketNewFrame, Serialized Form

      • getInlineScripts

        public ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript[] getInlineScripts(int execScope,
                                                   long dataRecordId)
        Get all inline scripts for a specific execution scope.
        Parameters:
        execScope - the selected execution scope of the inline scripts.
        dataRecordId - the data record ID of the referenced item inside the session, required only for EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_ITEM_START, EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_ITEM_END, EXEC_SCOPE_URL_START, EXEC_SCOPE_URL_END. Pass a value of -1 for all other execution scopes.
        Returns:
        an array of all selected inline scripts, sorted first by execution priority and second by script title (case insensitive)
        Since:
        V5.4-F
        See Also:
        ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_GLOBAL_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_GLOBAL_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_USER_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_USER_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_ITEM_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_LOOP_ITEM_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_URL_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_URL_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_ALL_URLS_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_ALL_URLS_END

      • getInlineScripts

        public ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript[] getInlineScripts(int[] execScopes,
                                                   long dataRecordId)
        Get all inline scripts that match to an array of specific execution scopes.
        Parameters:
        execScopes - an array of selected execution scopes of the inline scripts.

        Returns:
        an array of all selected inline scripts, sorted first by execution priority and second by script title (case insensitive)
        Since:
        V5.4-F
        See Also:
        ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_URL_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_URL_END, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_ALL_URLS_START, ProxySnifferVarSourceInlineScript.EXEC_SCOPE_ALL_URLS_END
